  "texts": [
    "Because impaired kidney function can cause the fluid overload, which increases the heart's workload and exacerbates heart failure symptoms.",
    "Moreover, kidney disease lead to high blood pressure and contribute to systemic inflammation, both of which further strain the heart and impair its function.",
    "(4) Unhealthy life habit can also increase the risk of heart failure.",
    "For example, alcohol dependence(303.93) and anxiety state(300.00) can cause the higher risk of heart failure.",
    "(5) Hypertension is another very important risk factor for heart failure."
